This is a reworked edition of surf_japan_v69.

Made for my clan; Nightmare

I tried to keep the size and feel of everything, al though I have made som slight changes to the gameplay. 

Everything has been redone, and those of you who experienced lag on the original map; you'll be pleased with this one.

I hope you all enjoy this map as much as I do.

Yours sincerely, razEr

PS:I will be doing a lot more maps like this. Remakes of popular combat /skill? maps. Look out. ;)
